name: StartShipFromStoreTask
description:
Starts a ShipFromStore task, identified by its UserTaskID.

The service returns the order that should be shipped from the user's current store as well as the OrderLines
that should be part of the shipment. Not necessarily all orderlines of the order should be shipped, so the
OrderLineIDs returned by this service should be respected.
auth_description: Requires a user of type `Employee` or `Api`

headers.description: The ID of the organization unit to run this request in.

F.name: Ranges
F.description:
The ranges of the shipping costs based on the order amount. Empty if shipping costs are determined using scripting or no ranges are known for the shipping method.
The ranges are non-overlapping, gapless and sorted by the minimum amount (ascending). The first range has a minimum amount of 0. The last range has a maximum amount of null.
